Salix flavida

    Authority   Chang & Skv.
      Family    Magnoliopsida:Dilleniidae:Violales:Salicaceae
     Synonyms
   Common names
      Editor
   Ecocrop code 9481

   Notes
   BRIEF DESCRIPTION
   Shrub.
   GROWING PERIOD
   Perennial.
   COMMON NAMES
   Salix flavida.
   FURTHER INF
   In the sandy deserts of northern China, salix flavida is grown as shawl
   for lee slopes. (pH estimated by the compiler).

   Sources
   SOURCES
   Walls J 1982 pp 70 [USE, TEMP, RAIN, TEXT, DEP]
   Shing T 1992 pp 323 [RAIN, TEXT]
   Westoby J 1975 pp 22 [TEMP, KTMP, DEP, FER, TEXT]

